# Teaching Whitelist for Berengario
# Users in this list can ADD content to the knowledge base via:
# - CC/BCC emails
# - Forwarded emails (if enabled)
#
# Copy this file to allowed_teachers.txt and customize for your deployment
#
# One email address or domain per line
# Lines starting with # are comments
# Domain wildcards: @imperial.ac.uk (allows all @imperial.ac.uk addresses)
# Individual addresses: alice@example.com

# Example: Department-wide teaching access
# @yourorganization.com

# Example: Specific authorized teachers
# alice@example.com
# bob@example.com
